  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>So long as you are exposed to at least 4 hours of sunlight per day, you no longer need to eat to survive and you gain +2 bonus on saves against diseases.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, you become immune to nonmagical diseases and no longer need to drink water to survive.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, you become immune to magical diseases, gain a +2 bonus on saving throws against poisons, and only need to sleep half as long to rest or recover from fatigue or exhaustion.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, you become immune to poison and fatigue. You lose these benefits if you fail to spend at least 4 hours in sunlight in a 24-hour period.</p>"
    },
